Here comes the collection Dhaka 

Dhaka is a traditional hand made fabric of the indigenous Limbu people of eastern Nepal. Dhaka patterns are as meaningful as they are unique, with each design carrying with it the history and stories of the Nepali people. Here  the showcasing of  collection made out of Dhaka which recite the story of just another talented Nepali girl, Farheen Waris who told me the description of Nepali Girls and made me ease while Transformation
